# This project's own runtime-generated files. ceo_engine_config.json and
# ceo_dashboard_auth.json in particular can hold the MT5 password,
# Telegram bot token, and the dashboard's auth password in plaintext
# (see dashboard.py's chmod 600 handling) -- these must never be
# committed, not just kept out by accident.
ceo_engine_config.json
ceo_dashboard_auth.json
ceo_trades.csv
ceo_trades_export.csv
ceo_engine.log
ceo_engine.log.*
ceo_journal.db
ceo_journal.db-wal
ceo_journal.db-shm
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

